                "key": "秘儀·律淵渡魂",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "秘儀·律淵渡魂"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成4點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>，<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">啟途誓使</span>的「憑依」級數+2。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">啟途誓使</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結束階段：</span>累積1級「憑依」。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">根據「憑依」級，提供效果：</span></p><p>大於等於2級：<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span>轉化為<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>；</p><p>大於等於4級：造成的傷害+2；</p><p>大於等於6級時：「憑依」級數-4。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/292125737/b6ab0891aede70ddf48bfa3859de14ea_5984687630779379704.png",
                "id": "talent20117",
                "key": "聖儀·煟煌隨狼行",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "聖儀·煟煌隨狼行"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">被動技能</span></p><p>【被動】戰鬥開始時，初始附屬<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">啟途誓使</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">啟途誓使</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結束階段：</span>累積1級「憑依」。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">根據「憑依」級，提供效果：</span></p><p>大於等於2級：<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span>轉化為<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>；</p><p>大於等於4級：造成的傷害+2；</p><p>大於等於6級時：「憑依」級數-4。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/292125737/8a173f8df2e58a9df74a6c3a74d385eb_9128235169874903141.png",
                "id": "talent3268",
                "key": "行度誓懲",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "行度誓懲"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超載</span>：本傷害+2，目標強制切換到下一個角色</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超導</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">感電</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">原激化</span>：本傷害+1，生成「<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">激化領域</span>」</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">激化領域</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span></p><p>我方對敵方出戰角色造成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素傷害</span>時，傷害值+1。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/23/84496276/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_793345502244001960.png",
